codeText: private boolean topDocsSortedByScore(TopDocs topDocs) {_        if (topDocs == null || topDocs.scoreDocs == null || topDocs.scoreDocs.length < 2) {_            return true__        }_        float lastScore = topDocs.scoreDocs[0].score__        for (int i = 1_ i < topDocs.scoreDocs.length_ i++) {_            ScoreDoc doc = topDocs.scoreDocs[i]__            if (Float.compare(doc.score, lastScore) > 0) {_                return false__            }_            lastScore = doc.score__        }_        return true__    }
